scenes.description: Natsuiro Matsuri performs a high-energy solo medley featuring remixes of 'Neo-Human', 'Godish', and 'INTERNET YAMERO'.
Transition sequence with concert graphics and applause.
Takanashi Kiara and IRyS perform their unit song 'SPICE'.
